OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FA butcher from Somerset brings a
OL,7,     Fmeaty lipoma on his neck for Dr
OL,8,     FDev Shah. Dr Toby Nelson has a
OL,9,     Fpatient with a skin condition
OL,10,     Faround her eyes.
OL,11,G0000 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,12,     FA devastating car crash leads to a
OL,13,     Fmanhunt for the driver and two
OL,14,     Fpassengers, at least one of whom
OL,15,     Fis bleeding heavily, and a
OL,16,     F13-year-old cyclist suffers a
OL,17,     Ftraumatic femur fracture.
